@node dw.wildfire

  ---------------------------------------------------------------------
  
     Wildfire - where dreams become virtuality - animations in 1996
  
  ---------------------------------------------------------------------

 Wildfire is a real professional program which offers unique features.
 Because it has for example more than 300 ARexx-commands it's
 impossible to create a complete features-list.

 Main features:

  -very fast converting
    input: @{" YAFA " link dw.yafa}, ANIM5, ANIM7S, ANIM7L, IFF-pictures
    output: @{" YAFA " link dw.yafa}, ANIM5, ANIM7S, ANIM7L, IFF-pictures

  -preview-function for all operations

  -project-editor with time-profile-editor which allows
   to create complicated projects with a few mouse-clicks

  -processor: this program-part is made for the power-user:
   it allows to create time-dependant special-effects
   using ADPro in a very easy way, another use is to import
   every picture-format into the converter or to convert
   an animation of the resultion 640x480x8 in another one
   with a resolution of 352x280x5
   (I'm sure - you wont want to miss it)

  -envelope-editor

  -timecodes-editor

  -powerful player-interface

  -nice animation-information-function which displays size-profiles etc.

  -all categories of generated data (animations,projects,processes,
   variables,envelopes,converter-sessions,annotations) can be loaded
   and saved to different user-defined locations with user-defined
   file-tags

  -font-sensitive GUI without MUI

  -ARexx-port

  -macros, custom-windows, docks

  - ...

  Wildfire will be released very soon through a commercial distributer! Read
  your Amiga-Magazines for more informations!

  Right now a limited test version was spread via Aminet. So put your hands
  on it NOW!

  ... and nor for our german readers...
  
  Das Programm verwandelt jeden Amiga der neuen Generation in
  ein Video-Studio, durch ein einzigartiges Konzept
  nutzt es jede mögliche Rechnerkonfiguration optimal aus.
  
  So können Sie auf einem Standard-A1200 mit 4 MB FASTRAM und
  100 MB Festplatte einen zehnminütigen vertonten Videoclip in
  voller Bildschirmgröße ablaufen lassen.
  
  Wollen Sie dagegen die Rechenpower ihres MC68060 einmal
  voll ausnutzen, so erzeugen sie atemberaubende Spezialeffekte
  oder spielen 3 Animationen gleichzeitig ab.
  
  Features:
   -eigenes Animationsformat dessen Stärke in der Flexibilität und
    Erweiterbarkeit liegt, so werden verschiedene Bildformate
    und Pack-Methoden unterstützt
   -volle Soundunterstützung (Module, Samples)
   -sehr schneller Converter, der auch zurückkonvertieren kann
   -einzigartiger Spezialeffekt-Generator, der das Programm
    ADPro benutzt
   -intuitiv zu bedienende fontsensitive Oberfläche, die keinen
    Ballast wie MUI benutzt
   -eine Online-Help, die keine Frage unbeantwortet läßt
   -optimales Preis/Leistungsverhältnis
  
  ----------------------------------------------------------------


@endnode


@node dw.yafa

 YAFA is THE new powerful animation-format for the Amiga-computer-
 series of the new generation. Unlike the popular formats like
 "ANIM" or "SSA" the internal representation of the graphical
 data isn't fixed. So it's possible to create animations which
 run fast on every machine. Because of the realtime-zoom-feature
 you can now create full-screen-animations on your A1200 which
 run at 50 fps.

 The program "yp" has all features a animation-player
 should have and many more:

  -animations can be load directly from harddisk or from ram
  -projects: This is a very amazing feature: you can
   append as many animations as you want and play them
   as one. So you can create your own video-clips easily !
  -realtime-zooming
  -sound-effects: PT-modules, IFF-samples (mono and stereo)
  - ...


 YAFA is part of the @{" Wildfire " link dw.wildfire} package. A free
 version of the player is available on the Aminet, so everyone is able
 to use this fantastic animation format!

@endnode
